<template>
  <div class="bv-example-row">
    <b-container>
      <b-row>
        <b-card no body class="overflow-hidden">
          <b-row no-gutters>
            <b-card-body>
              <b-form ref="form">
                <b-row>
                  <b-col cols="12 mb-4" sm="4" style="margin: auto">
                    <b-form-group invalid-feedback="Campo Vazio">
                      <b-form-input
                        id="Referência"
                        v-model="paramsBusca"
                        placeholder="Referência"
                        rows="3"
                        max-rows="6"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12 mb-4" sm="8" style="margin: auto">
                    <b-form-group>
                      <b-button
                        variant="primary"
                        block
                        @click="BuscaParamInjecao()"
                      >
                        Buscar
                      </b-button>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                </b-row>
                <b-row>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="NumeroMolde"
                      label="Molde"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        label-for="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.NumeroMolde"
                        disabled="true"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Altura"
                      label="Altura"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="Altura"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Altura"
                        disabled="true"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Comprimento"
                      label="Comprimento"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="Comprimento"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Comprimento"
                        disabled="true"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Largura"
                      label="Largura"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Largura"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="CursoExtrassao"
                      label="Curso Extrassão"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.CursoExtrassao"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group id="peso" label="Peso" label-for="input-2">
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.peso"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Cavidades"
                      label="Cavidades"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Cavidades"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="NumeroInjetora"
                      label="Número Injetora"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.NumeroInjetora"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group id="Data" label="Data" label-for="input-2">
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Data"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Temperatura"
                      label="Temperatura"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Temperatura"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="CicloTotal"
                      label="Ciclo Total"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.CicloTotal"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="TempoInjecao"
                      label="Tempo Injeção"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.TempoInjecao"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Temporecalque"
                      label="Tempo recalque"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Temporecalque"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="SoproFixo"
                      label="Sopro Fixo"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.TempoExtSoproFixo"
                        disabled="true"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>

                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="TempoExtSoproMovel"
                      label="Sopro Movel"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.TempoExtSoproMovel"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Reciclo"
                      label="Reciclo"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Reciclo"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="TempoResfriamento"
                      label="Resfriamento"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.TempoResfriamento"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="PressaoSegMolde"
                      label="Segurança"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.PressaoSegMolde"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="PressaoTravamento"
                      label="Travamento"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.PressaoTravamento"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="PressaoavancoExtrator"
                      label="Pressão Extrator"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.PressaoavancoExtrator"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="PressaorecuoInjecao"
                      label="Pressão Recuo"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.PressaorecuoInjecao"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="TempoExtSoproFixo"
                      label="Sopro Fixo"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.CursoAberturaMolde"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="CursoAvancoExtrator"
                      label="Curso Extrator"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.CursoAvancoExtrator"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="InicioProtMolde"
                      label="Proteção"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        class="form-input"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.InicioProtMolde"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="RecuoUniInjecao"
                      label="RecuoUniInjecao"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.RecuoUniInjecao"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="pressaoMachos"
                      label="pressaoMachos"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        class="form-input"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.pressaoMachos"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="velMachos"
                      label="Vel Machos"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.velMachos"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="posicaoMachos"
                      label="Posição Machos"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.posicaoMachos"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Tempomachos"
                      label="Machos"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Tempomachos"
                        disabled="true"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="ModoInjecao"
                      label="Modo Injecao"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        class="form-input"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.ModoInjecao"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="BicoInjecao"
                      label="Bico Injecao"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        class="form-input"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.BicoInjecao"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group id="Horas" label="Horas" label-for="input-2">
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Horas"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="TipoMP1"
                      label="Tipo MP1"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        class="form-input"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.TipoMP1"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="PercMateriaPrima1"
                      label="% 1"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.PercMateriaPrima1"
                        disabled="true"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="TipoMP2"
                      label="Tipo MP2"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.TipoMP2"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="PercMateriaPrima2"
                      label="% 2"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.PercMateriaPrima2"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="TipoMP3"
                      label="Tipo MP3"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.TipoMP3"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="PercMateriaPrima3"
                      label="% 3"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.PercMateriaPrima3"
                        disabled="true"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="DispSeguranca"
                      label="Segurança"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.DispSeguranca"
                        disabled="true"
                        class="form-input"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                  <b-col cols="12" sm="2">
                    <b-form-group
                      id="Estufagem"
                      label="Estufagem"
                      label-for="input-2"
                    >
                      <b-form-input
                        id="input-2"
                        v-model="paraminjecao.Estufagem"
                        class="form-input"
                        disabled="true"
                      ></b-form-input>
                    </b-form-group>
                  </b-col>
                </b-row>
              </b-form>

              <b-card header="Temperatura Programada" class="table-layout">
                <b-table
                  hover
                  striped
                  small
                  :items="paraminjecao.TempProgramadaInjecao"
                  :fields="TemperaturaProgramada"
                >
                </b-table>
              </b-card>
              <p></p>
              <b-row>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="3">
                  <b-card header="Injeção" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemInjecao"
                      :fields="fields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="3">
                  <b-card header="Recalque" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemRecalque"
                      :fields="fields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="3">
                  <b-card header="Dosagem" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemDosagem"
                      :fields="fields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="3">
                  <b-card header="Descompressão" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemDescompressao"
                      :fields="fields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
              </b-row>
              <p></p>
              <b-row>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="3">
                  <b-card header="Sequencial" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemBicosSequenciais"
                      :fields="fields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="3">
                  <b-card header="Machos" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemTempMachos"
                      :fields="fields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="3">
                  <b-card header="Fechamento" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemFechamento"
                      :fields="fields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="3">
                  <b-card header="Extração" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemExtracao"
                      :fields="fields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
              </b-row>
              <p></p>
              <b-row>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="6">
                  <b-card header="Refrigeração" class="table-layout">
                    <b-table
                      hover
                      striped
                      small
                      :items="paraminjecao.TipoRegulagemRefrigeracao"
                      :fields="RefrigeracaoFields"
                    >
                    </b-table>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
                <b-col cols="12" sm="6">
                  <b-card header="Observação" class="table-layout">
                    <b-form-textarea
                      class="table-layout"
                      id="textarea-auto-height"
                      rows="3"
                      max-rows="8"
                      v-model="paraminjecao.OBS"
                    ></b-form-textarea>
                  </b-card>
                </b-col>
              </b-row>
            </b-card-body>
          </b-row>
        </b-card>
      </b-row>
    </b-container>
  </div>
</template>

<script>
import API from "../../../services/api.service";

export default {
  name: "ParametroInjecao",
  data() {
    return {
      paramsBusca: "",
      paraminjecao: {
        TipoRegulagemInjecao: [],
        TipoRegulagemRecalque: [],
        TipoRegulagemDosagem: [],
        TipoRegulagemDescompressao: [],
        TipoRegulagemBicosSequenciais: [],
        TipoRegulagemTempMachos: [],
        TipoRegulagemFechamento: [],
        TipoRegulagemExtracao: [],
        TipoRegulagemRefrigeracao: [],
        TemperaturaProgramada: [],
      },
      fields: [
        {
          key: "Tipo",
          label: "Tipo",
          thClass: "text-left tableCellSM",
          tdClass: "tableCellSM",
        },
        {
          key: "valor",
          label: "Valor",
          thClass: "text-left tableCellSM",
          tdClass: "tableCellSM",
        },
      ],
      RefrigeracaoFields: [
        {
          key: "AguaOleo",
          label: "Agua/Oleo",
          thClass: "text-left tableCellSM",
          tdClass: "tableCellSM",
        },
        {
          key: "NormalGelada",
          label: "Normal/Gelada",
          thClass: "text-left tableCellSM",
          tdClass: "tableCellSM",
        },
        {
          key: "Lado",
          label: "Lado",
          thClass: "text-left tableCellSM",
          tdClass: "tableCellSM",
        },
        {
          key: "valor",
          label: "Valor",
          thClass: "text-left tableCellSM",
          tdClass: "tableCellSM",
        },
      ],
      TemperaturaProgramada: [
        {
          key: "TipoTemperatura",
          label: "Tipo",
          thClass: "text-left tableCellSM",
          tdClass: "tableCellSM",
          variant: "secondary",
        },
        { key: "Temp1", label: "1" },
        { key: "Temp2", label: "2", variant: "secondary" },
        { key: "Temp3", label: "3" },
        { key: "Temp4", label: "4", variant: "secondary" },
        { key: "Temp5", label: "5" },
        { key: "Temp6", label: "6", variant: "secondary" },
        { key: "Temp7", label: "7" },
        { key: "Temp8", label: "8", variant: "secondary" },
        { key: "Temp9", label: "9" },
        { key: "Temp10", label: "10", variant: "secondary" },
        { key: "Temp11", label: "11" },
        { key: "Temp12", label: "12", variant: "secondary" },
        { key: "Temp13", label: "13" },
        { key: "Temp14", label: "14", variant: "secondary" },
        { key: "Temp15", label: "15" },

  },
  methods: {

        if (api.data.Success == "True" || api.data.Success) {

        } else {

      });
    },
  },
};
